Description: 2D animation software
 Enve is a 2D animation software with support for vector and raster graphics.
 It features a node-based workflow, advanced animation tools, and support
 for various export formats including video and image sequences.
 .
 Features:
  - Vector and raster graphics support
  - Node-based compositing
  - Advanced animation tools
  - FFmpeg video export
  - Skia graphics engine
